<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      body {
          font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
          line-height: 1.6;
          color: #ffffff;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          background-color: #181C14;
      }
      .container {
          max-width: 600px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
          background-color: #272624;
          padding: 20px;
          text-align: center;
          border-bottom: 2px solid #3B3B3B;
      }
      .header h1 {
          color: #EBCB00;
          font-size: 2rem;
          font-weight: 600;
          margin: 0;
      }
      .rejection-banner {
          background-color: #A04747;
          color: #fff;
          padding: 15px;
          text-align: center;
          border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          font-weight: 500;
      }
      .content {
          padding: 20px;
          background-color: #272624;
          border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .section {
          background-color: #171616;
          padding: 15px;
          border-radius: 5px;
          margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .section h3 {
          color: #EBCB00;
          font-size: 1.25rem;
          font-weight: 600;
          margin-top: 0;
      }
      .services-list {
          list-style-type: none;
          padding-left: 0;
          margin: 0;
      }
      .services-list li {
          padding: 8px 0;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #3B3B3B;
      }
      .services-list li:last-child {
          border-bottom: none;
      }
      p, li {
        color: #fff
      }
      .reason-box {
          background-color: #2E3266;
          border-radius: 5px;
          padding: 15px;
          margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
          text-align: center;
          padding: 20px;
          font-size: 0.75rem;
          color: #9E9E9E;
      }
      strong {
          color: #EBCB00;
      }
      .booking-id {
          text-align: center;
          font-size: 1.1rem;
          color: #9E9E9E;
          margin: 10px 0;
      }
      .alternative-suggestion {
          background-color: #2E704A;
          padding: 15px;
          border-radius: 5px;
          margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .search-button {
          display: inline-block;
          padding: 12px 24px;
          background-color: #EBCB00;
          color: #272624;
          text-decoration: none;
          border-radius: 5px;
          margin: 20px 0;
          font-weight: 500;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          font-size: 0.875rem;
      }
      .search-button:hover {
          background-color: #EBD226;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Booking Request Update</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="rejection-banner">
        We could not accept your booking request
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= user.name %>,</p>

        <p>
          We regret to inform you that your parking booking request could not be
          accepted at this time.
        </p>

        <div class="booking-id">Booking Request ID: #<%= bookingId %></div>

        <div class="section">
          <h3>Requested Booking Details:</h3>
          <p><strong>Location: </strong> <%= parkingLocation %></p>
          <p><strong>Parking Slot: </strong> <%= parkingSlot %></p>
          <p><strong>Date: </strong> <%= bookingDate %></p>
          <p><strong>Start Time: </strong> <%= startTime %></p>
          <p><strong>End Time: </strong> <%= endTime %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="reason-box">
          <h3>Reason for Rejection:</h3>
          <p><%= rejectionReason %></p>
        </div>

        <center>
          <a href="<%= searchUrl %>" class="search-button">
            Search Other Parking Spaces
          </a>
        </center>

        <p>
          We understand this may be inconvenient for you. Here are some steps
          you can take:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Try booking for a different time slot</li>
          <li>Check availability at nearby parking locations</li>
          <li>
            Contact our support team for assistance in finding alternatives
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>We appreciate your understanding.</p>
        <p>If you need assistance, our support team is here to help.</p>
        <p>
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> YourParkingApp. All rights
          reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
